    • Uses of Collidable in game.gameObject.physics

      Methods in game.gameObject.physics with parameters of type Collidable 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void Collidable.hasCollided(Collidable collisionObject)
      This method is called when this object has collided with another Collidable object.
      void Collidable.noLongerColliding(Collidable collidedObject)
      This method is called when this object exits a collision.
      void Collidable.willCollide(Collidable collisionObject)
      This method is called when the next update(long) method call will cause this object to collide with another Collidable object.
      void Collidable.willNoLongerCollide(Collidable collidedObject)
      This method is called when the next update(long) method call will cause this object to exit a collision.
